Class DefaultAstrocyte

java.lang.Object
prkmodel.types.templates.AbstractNervousSystemElement
prkmodel.types.templates.DefaultAstrocyte
All Implemented Interfaces:
Astrocyte, NervousSystemElement
Direct Known Subclasses:
RepastAstrocyte
public class DefaultAstrocyte extends AbstractNervousSystemElement implements Astrocyte
Default implementation of the Astrocyte interface. Represents an astrocyte in the nervous system with default behaviors and properties.

To implement a subclass:

  • Ensure the constructor properly initializes inherited fields.
  • Override methods to provide specific behavior.
  • Document the purpose of any new methods or overridden methods.
  • Use super to call the superclass method when overriding to extend or modify its behavior.
